text: Marc Larimer (December 28, 1890 - February 6, 1919) was an American fencer. He competed in the individual foil and épée events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1890 births Category:1919 deaths Category:American male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of the United States Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Wichita, Kansas
